title: 'Boys and Girl - Week 10 Vikings Preview; Dak's Built For Dallas; Amari's Health; Dallas Morning News Reporter Calvin Watkins
itunes:title: 'Boys and Girl - Week 10 Vikings Preview; Dak's Built For Dallas; Amari's Health; Dallas Morning News Reporter Calvin Watkins
description:
On today’s episode of the 'Boys and Girl Podcast, Jane and Bobby break down why Dak Prescott is uniquely equipped to be the quarterback of America’s Team. Also, what’s the latest on Amari Cooper’s health? Plus, Dallas Morning News reporter Calvin Watkins stops by. Follow Jane and Bobby on Twitter and subscribe to get all the latest inside information from two of the most connected people in the Cowboys' community.
